# arvo-hash

L2 hash-domain types and algorithm contracts. `ContentHash` aliases
arvo `Bits<28, Hot>` for call-site domain naming. Generic streaming
`Hasher<const N: Width>` trait with blanket `HasherExt<const N:
Width>` for oneshot ergonomics lets downstream code parameterise
over algorithm choice. Ships `Fnv1a<const N: Width>` (FNV-1a-64
algorithm with `N <= 64` const-eval guard) as the first concrete
algorithm; further algorithms (xxHash, CRC32) ship as additional
trait implementors. `#![no_std]`, no alloc.
